### Login with valid credentials
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testrest1@example.com",
  "password": "securePass123"
}



### Create client
POST http://localhost:3000/api/client
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ACME Corp",
  "email": "contact@acme.com",
  "phone": "+123456789",
  "address": "123 Main Street"
}

### Create project
POST http://localhost:3000/api/project
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client_id": 1,
  "name": "Website Redesign",
  "description": "Full UI/UX overhaul"
}


### List my projects
GET http://localhost:3000/api/project
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>



### Get project by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/project/1
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>



### Update project
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/project/1
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Website",
  "description": "Phase 2 scope"
}


### Archive project
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/project/1/archive
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>



### Restore project
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/project/1/restore
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>


### Hard delete project
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/project/1
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>
